Subject: tools headers UAPI: Sync linux/prctl.h with the kernel sources
Git-commit: 49024204322cbfff892a28a67ad813cd41b6be81
Patch-mainline: v5.16-rc1
References: bsc#1194659

To pick the changes in:

  61bc346ce64a3864 ("uapi/linux/prctl: provide macro definitions for the PR_SCHED_CORE type argument")

That don't result in any changes in tooling:

  $ tools/perf/trace/beauty/prctl_option.sh > before
  $ cp include/uapi/linux/prctl.h tools/include/uapi/linux/prctl.h
  $ tools/perf/trace/beauty/prctl_option.sh > after
  $ diff -u before after
  $

Just silences this perf tools build warning:

  Warning: Kernel ABI header at 'tools/include/uapi/linux/prctl.h' differs from latest version at 'include/uapi/linux/prctl.h'
  diff -u tools/include/uapi/linux/prctl.h include/uapi/linux/prctl.h

